{"type": "article", "id": 17918, "title": "可耐力材料的“充气椅”", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-23T06:53:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606160157xQ1aA3ilGgJuKeNt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是伦敦设计师 Rachel Harding 带来“充气椅”，实际上是将空气充进了可耐力材料里，让椅子可以像花岗岩一样坚固。在高温下，可耐力材料可以变得很柔软，填进空气后有气球的膨胀感，冷却后又重新变成坚固的材料。Rachel Harding 使用了三维建模软件设计了这款充满未来感的椅子，也是对材料的新探索。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261449403Ius4pEXoJwPNFRe.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144941yLBFXHvjg4Ita1iZ.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144941JdHtzTqrE6LcnFiO.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144942NVdfC8hycGKkLt7X.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261449424R3oXczd1rYIg2Su.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"527\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}